OL,3,CPolice search for suspect with burns
OL,4,Cafter 'arson' attack
OL,6,FPolice are searching for a suspect
OL,7,Fwith burn injuries after a reported
OL,8,Farson attack on a car in Dorset.
OL,10,FDorset Police were called by the fire
OL,11,Fservice at 11.20pm on Thursday 9 April
OL,12,F2026 to reports of a car fire on South
OL,13,FAvenue in Sherborne.
OL,15,FAnother report was made that the fire
OL,16,Fhad spread to a nearby property and
OL,17,Ffences. One person was taken to
OL,18,Fhospital having suffered smoke
OL,19,Finhalation.
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G1/4
