CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F435A1776103865
OL,3,CPolice search for suspect with burns
OL,4,Cafter 'arson' attack
OL,6,FPolice officers have been working with
OL,7,Fthe fire service and believe the fire
OL,8,Fwas started deliberately.
OL,10,FDetective Inspector Rich Barnett, from
OL,11,FDorset County CID, said: "I am keen to
OL,12,Fhear from anyone who witnessed any
OL,13,Fsuspicious activity in the area around
OL,14,Fthe relevant time and would also ask
OL,15,Fresidents in the vicinity of South
OL,16,FAvenue and Lenthay Road to please
OL,17,Freview any home CCTV or doorbell
OL,18,Fcamera footage from around 9.10pm to
OL,19,F11.20pm on Thursday 9 April 2026.
OL,26,@sD@ZOU
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G2/4
