PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F435A1776103865
OL,3,CPolice search for suspect with burns
OL,4,Cafter 'arson' attack
OL,6,F"From our enquiries we also believe a
OL,7,Fmale suspect from the scene may have
OL,8,Fsustained superficial injuries from
OL,9,Fthe fire. I would urge anyone who has
OL,10,Fconcerns around a man who has
OL,11,Fsustained suspected burn injuries in
OL,12,Funexplained circumstances to please
OL,13,Fget in touch.
OL,15,F"Local officers have been carrying out
OL,16,Fadditional patrols in this area since
OL,17,Fthe fire and can be approached by
OL,18,Fmembers of the public with information
OL,19,For concerns."
OL,26,@nD@AOUwD@AOU{D@MO]
